{{champion:154}} size scales with his health, this would be about the same thing.

I think you are overthinking this. Ultimates don't really have evolving effects, they have evolving _models_. This would just be a special effect change based on stacks, only slightly more complicated than what Zac has. Although the lightning might be a bit much...

Now, while we are talking about Theme QoL changes WHEN IS XERATH GETTING A REAL ULT? I'm tired of the peashooter ;-;

